    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the risotto is cooking, zest of<strong> half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
