    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>When the risotto is almost ready, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and cook for 10-12 min or until slightly charred and tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
