      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy 'Nduja risotto </strong>in bowls and top with the <strong>pan-fried Tenderstem</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>lemon zest </strong>over the Tenderstem broccoli – this is<strong> your zesty Tenderstem broccoli</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
